body.description: For Google Pixel 8 Pro privacy screen protector enables you to enjoy your privacy space better, and provides maximum protection for your phone, including anti daily scrape, anti stain, and reduce the chance of screen cracking due to drops. Features: ● Anti-spy: The screen image is visible in the direction of 90 degrees from the front of your phone, but not visible outside the area that is 35degrees to the left or the right. ● Support ultrasonic fingerprint ID. Response quickly. ● Made of ultra-thin and ultra-smooth Tempering Glass material, it maintains the high sensitivity and responsiveness of the original screen, providing you with a smooth and fluid touch experience. ● With excellent flexibility and unique shock-absorbing layer structure design, it can effectively decompose impact and external pressure to protect the screen. ● Perfect protection: It will be your best choice because it can provide edge-to-edge protection for your device. ● Anti-fingerprint and anti-greasy: The surface is treated with plasma oleophobic coating, so it can effectively reduce fingerprint smudges, oil and dust. Keep the screen clean as new. ● Self-healing: Scratch-resistant and bubble-free. ● Case friendly: Its precise size makes your phone compatible with most phone cases. Attention: ● Because of the anti-peeping feature, the brightness of the screen will be reduced while using the film. If you wish to enjoy a better experience, we suggest that you adjust the brightness of your phone. ● Before applying the film, please watch the installation video carefully and follow the instructions. ● If there are tiny bubbles, don't worry. They will disappear automatically within 24 hours. ● It is recommended that you update the fingerprint ID again after finishing the installation so that it can be more sensitively recognized.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 12, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Worst screen protector I've ever purchased
reviews.reviewText: I buy screen protectors for all my phones, and whenever they break I replace them. This is probably the worst one I've ever purchased in 10 years, of over 20 different screen protectors I've purchased over those years.The kit comes with two screen protectors but only enough components like alcohol wipes and dust removing stickers for one screen to be installed.The kit is the most bare bones I've ever seen. No alignment tools, no tools for removing air bubbles. The instructions were a joke.The thumb print scanner on the screen protector is made of different glass and you can clearly tell. There's a giant very visible circle on my phone.The glass for the screen protector seems to smudge extremely easy. I understand that that's usually the case with screen protectors because it's not quite the same grade of glass as the cell phone, this is just really bad.The camera lens protector doesn't stick properly. Full of air bubbles.

reviews.reviewText: This product is easy to install and it certainly lights up an area. Added it to my attic and garage and what a difference it makes.
